Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:57.49,Rainbow Star lyrics,,0,0,0,,Destrua a triste realidade que reflete em seus olhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:02:02.74,Rainbow Star lyrics,,0,0,0,,Vamos levantar nossas asas, cheias de calor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.70,Rainbow Star lyrics,,0,0,0,,Anjos caídos surreais,
